OL,3,CLFC Foundation and Forever Reds rally
OL,4,Cbehind a foodbank after Anfield theft
OL,6,FLiverpool FC has come together to
OL,7,Fsupport a charity after one if its
OL,8,Ffundraising buckets was stolen from
OL,9,Foutside of Anfield.
OL,11,FThe club's official charity, the LFC
OL,12,FFoundation, and Forever Reds - the
OL,13,Fclub's former players association -
OL,14,Fhave donated #5,000 to Fans Supporting
OL,15,FFoodbanks following the theft.
OL,17,FThe theft, which took place ahead of
OL,18,Fthe Paris Saint-Germain game on 14
OL,19,FApril, prompted an immediate
OL,20,Foutpouring of support from the local
OL,21,Fcommunity and the wider club family.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
