PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777021560
OL,3,CLFC Foundation and Forever Reds rally
OL,4,Cbehind a foodbank after Anfield theft
OL,6,FIt says the donation "underlines
OL,7,FLiverpool FC's ongoing commitment" to
OL,8,Fits local communities and acknowledges
OL,9,F"the essential work Fans Supporting
OL,10,FFoodbanks do, especially on match days
OL,11,Fto tackle food poverty across
OL,12,FLiverpool and beyond".
OL,14,FLast season LFC Foundation supported
OL,15,F145,617 people, with more than half
OL,16,Fcoming from the top 20% most-deprived
OL,17,Fareas in the country.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777021560
OL,3,CLFC Foundation and Forever Reds rally
OL,4,Cbehind a foodbank after Anfield theft
OL,6,FThrough its Red Neighbours initiative,
OL,7,Fthe Foundation also donated over
OL,8,F#500,000 in essential food hampers,
OL,9,Fstadium tours, and matchday
OL,10,Fexperiences, as well as providing
OL,11,F1,000 free meals per week to local
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FMatt Parish, CEO of LFC Foundation,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Fans Supporting Foodbanks are
OL,16,Fan outstanding example of the power of
OL,17,Ffootball to make a positive difference
OL,18,Fin our communities.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
