FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777021560
OL,3,CLFC Foundation and Forever Reds rally
OL,4,Cbehind a foodbank after Anfield theft
OL,6,F"Their volunteers give so much of
OL,7,Ftheir time to help others, and the
OL,8,Fwork they do is more important than
OL,9,Fever. We're proud to support them
OL,10,Falongside Forever Reds and to stand
OL,11,Fwith them following this incident."
OL,13,FThe Foundation supported the delivery
OL,14,Fof 1,000 free meals per week, prepared
OL,15,Fby the LFC kitchens, to community
OL,16,Fmember.
OL,26,@sD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
