PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777021560
OL,3,CLFC Foundation and Forever Reds rally
OL,4,Cbehind a foodbank after Anfield theft
OL,6,FForever Reds Chair, John Aldridge,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I'm incredibly proud that
OL,8,FForever Reds can support this great
OL,9,Fcause. Fans Supporting Foodbanks do
OL,10,Funbelievable work week in, week out,
OL,11,Fand when something like this happens,
OL,12,Fwe all must pull together and show
OL,13,Fwhat Liverpool Football Club is really
OL,14,Fabout.
OL,16,F"This is a brilliant initiative run by
OL,17,Famazing people, and we're delighted to
OL,18,Fbe able to help."
OL,26,@zD@QO]
